# Example environment variable *names* for SchwabMCP.
# Copy into your MCP host env, OS environment, or user-secrets — never commit real values.
#
#   dotnet user-secrets set "Schwab:AppKey" "YOUR_APP_KEY" --project src/SchwabMCP
#   dotnet user-secrets set "Schwab:AppSecret" "YOUR_APP_SECRET" --project src/SchwabMCP
#
# Required
#   Schwab__AppKey
#   Schwab__AppSecret
#
# Optional
#   Schwab__CallbackUrl          default https://127.0.0.1:8182
#   Schwab__TokenStorePath       default under LocalApplicationData/SchwabMCP
#   Schwab__RefreshToken         headless only; prefer OAuth + local token store
#
# See docs/authentication.md
